  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the Retrowave Universe!<br>Drive through your favorite Retrowave scenes and enjoy music composed especially for you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669130/extras/1edb907a7a586753672a741a322639c8.poster.avif?t=1627043607\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669130/extras/1edb907a7a586753672a741a322639c8.webm?t=1627043607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669130/extras/1edb907a7a586753672a741a322639c8.mp4?t=1627043607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The universe reacts to your actions!<br>Shoot the cubes and you will keep the Retrowave vibe. Miss or crash and you will see how it vanishes away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669130/extras/4ae160a9f42905b488bb8baa6023d933.poster.avif?t=1627043607\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669130/extras/4ae160a9f42905b488bb8baa6023d933.webm?t=1627043607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669130/extras/4ae160a9f42905b488bb8baa6023d933.mp4?t=1627043607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Race or relax, the choice is yours!<br>The faster you go the more dangerous your ride is, but it might be worth it if you want to unlock all cars and paint jobs as fast as possible.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669130/extras/cad3d10de3dee08365263d93c23822b8.poster.avif?t=1627043607\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669130/extras/cad3d10de3dee08365263d93c23822b8.webm?t=1627043607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669130/extras/cad3d10de3dee08365263d93c23822b8.mp4?t=1627043607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
